Output assets/demo.gif
Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Sleep 500ms
Type "# AI Coding Battles in your terminal"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "arena battle fizzbuzz --left qwen --right deepseek"
Enter
Sleep 30s

Type "arena leaderboard"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "arena bench qwen --challenges fizzbuzz,binary-search --json | head -20"
Enter
Sleep 15s
